        <num>CCP 4235</num>
        <heading>4235.  Authority and liability of tutor after resignation or removal</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 4235.  Authority and liability of tutor after resignation or removal
A tutor who has resigned or has been removed shall have no further authority as such, and no further duty except as provided by Article 4392.  However, his liability for acts prior to his resignation or removal shall not be affected thereby.</p>
        </content>
